query:
SELECT 
        "id",
        "providerSource" as provider_source, 
        "userId" as user_id,
        "resourceId" as resource_id
      FROM "InsightContext"
      WHERE
        "userId" = $1
      AND
        "providerSource" = $2
      AND
        "consumed" = false
      ORDER BY
        "createdAt" DESC
      LIMIT
        $3
